     * @param b FRI commitment (polynomial low-degree proof)
     * @param c Evaluation commitment (constraint polynomial evaluations)
     * @param publicSignals Public witness data from AIR (Algebraic Intermediate Representation)
     * @return Whether proof is valid
     */
